      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/99/5473",
      "text": [
        " \"اَلشَّيْءُ فِي كِتَابِ عَلِيٍّ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ وَاحِدٌ مِنْ سِتَّةٍ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5473 - Aban ibn Taghlib narrated from Imam Ali ibn Al-Hussain (as) that Imam (as) was asked about a man who made a bequest (waṣiyyah) of something from his wealth.\nImam (as) replied: \"The portion specified in the Book of (Imam) Ali (as) is one out of six parts.\""
        ]
      }
    },
